artists/mark-hoppus">马克·霍普斯</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-barker-on-strained-blink-182-relationship-it-was-always-heavy-on-my-heart-3518039">的紧张关系</a>，称这“总是让我心沉重”。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-barker-gets-his-own-wax-figure-at-madame-tussauds-it-looks-so-fucking-real-3519818">杜莎夫人蜡像馆还为他提供了一座新蜡像</a>。</p><p> Blink-182 的特拉维斯<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">·</a> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blink-182s-travis-barker-says-power-of-love-helped-him-overcome-fear-of-flying-3525928">巴克 (Travis Barker) 表示，“爱的力量”帮助他克服了对飞行的恐惧</a>。</p> ;
